<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.247576>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Melanoplus trachodes n. sp. Male head, pronotum, thorax in left lateral view (a) and head and pronotum in dorsal view (b); left cercus in lateral view (c); distal segments of male abdomen in dorsal view (d); epiphallus in dorsal view (e) and phallic complex without epiphallus in dorsal view (f)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/247576/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.247585>
    dc:description "FIGURE 24. Melanoplus reflexus. Male head, pronotum, thorax in left lateral view (a) and head and pronotum in dorsal view (b); left cercus in lateral view (c); distal segments of male abdomen in dorsal view (d); epiphallus in dorsal view (e); phallic complex without epiphallus in dorsal view (f)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/247585/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.247578>
    dc:description "FIGURE 17. Melanoplus trachodes n. sp., male’ internal genitalia: phallic complex without epiphallus in dorsal view (a), phallic complex without epiphallus in lateral view (b), distal portion of aedeagus’ valves in ventral view (c), epiphallus in dorsal view (d), epiphallus in lateral view (e)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/247578/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.247583>
    dc:description "FIGURE 22. Melanoplus trachodes n. sp., living female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/247583/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.247584>
    dc:description "FIGURE 23. Melanoplus trachodes n. sp., living female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/247584/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.247580>
    dc:description "FIGURE 19. Melanoplus trachodes n. sp., female’s cercus and ovipositor valvae (a), distribution map (b)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/247580/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.247587>
    dc:description "FIGURE 26. Melanoplus reflexus, female’s cercus and ovipositor’s valvae." ;
